# Contact form email delivery (Resend — https://resend.com)
#
# When a visitor submits the contact form, it is emailed to support@fidelabs.io.
# No email is sent to the visitor.
#
# Setup (no domain / no DNS needed):
#   1. Sign up at resend.com using support@fidelabs.io as the account email.
#   2. Create an API key at https://resend.com/api-keys and paste it below.
# That's the only value you must set.

RESEND_API_KEY=

# --- Optional overrides (defaults are built into the code, leave blank) ---
# CONTACT_TO_EMAIL   — inbox that receives submissions. Default: support@fidelabs.io
# CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL — the required "From" address on the email. Default:
#   onboarding@resend.dev (Resend's shared sender; delivers to your Resend
#   account email, so no domain setup is needed). Only override this after
#   verifying fidelabs.io at resend.com/domains, e.g.
#   CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL="FIDE Website <noreply@fidelabs.io>"
